Class TreePath

  • Object
    • TreePath

  • public class TreePath
extends Object
    Class that represents a path to an element in the tree of artist alternate name manual overrides.

    Pivot already includes a Path class for this purpose, but I'm using the path as the key in a HashMap, which requires an equals method, which Pivot's class does not have.

    Author:
    Jon
